# IndonesiaNFT.org

## We help Indonesian artists mint their first NFT for free.

We are a non-profit volunteer movement with a firm belief in decentralization. 

We don't mint NFTs for you, you mint them yourself and retain full control (and responsibility).

We help you for free with tech support and minting fees on the xDai marketplace.

# SNAFU Collective

SNAFU is an Italian collective of artists composed of cyberpunks, painters, graphic designers, programmers, photographers, musicians, art lovers who try to create a unique point of view regarding what can be conceived like Art in an era where everything is digital and unsubstantial.

At the same time, we are driven by the desire of creating a new form of sustenance for emerging artists exploiting new paradigms that blockchain and cryptocurrencies had brought
